data.description: Welcome to this cozy & serene condo in the well sought after Sienna Villas! This resort style complex is based in a prime location in Valencia. Within close proximity to the Valencia Mall, Whole Foods, and restaurants! Close to the freeway, biking trails, College Of The Canyons, public transportation, Henry Mayo Hospital, and more. This upper-level unit offers two bedrooms & two bathrooms with an open concept living room that makes for a great gathering space! The kitchen offers white cabinets, tile backsplash, appliances, and a breakfast bar. The dining area is adjoined by the kitchen and has extra cabinets for storage. Enjoy your morning coffee on the patio and in the serenity of nature. This well manicured complex consists of three pools and two tennis courts. This unit is assigned two parking spots in the subterranean garage with private remote access. There is ample guest parking spaces for visitors as well. HOA includes water, trash, sewer, landscape, and pest control of common areas. NO MELLO ROOS. Schedule a showing to see all this community has to offer!
